		<Section title='About'>
			<p class='text-muted-foreground'>
				Software Engineer specializing in backend cloud software architecture, development and
				building cloud-native applications. Experienced in architecting solutions in AWS and
				full-stack development.
			</p>
		</Section>

		<Section title='Experience'>
			<Card
				heading='Dyson'
				subheading='Senior Cloud Software Engineer'
				date='Sept 2023 - Present'
				imagePath='/src/assets/dyson.png'
				altText='Lorem, ipsum dolor sit'
				imageClass='h-12 w-auto md:-left-16'
			>
