						Built an internal content management service to enable business functions to manage
						assets for MyDyson App.
					</li>
					<li>
						Built a content serving service to that serves assets to MyDyson App used by millions
						worldwide.
					</li>
					<li>
						Developed and maintained metric pipeline that provides daily user usage metrics from
						MyDyson app to support key business functions.
					</li>
				</ul>
