					Designed, built, and maintained cloud-native applications on AWS, utilizing technologies
					such as Serverless, Appsync GraphQL, RDS, and DynamoDB, with a focus on Typescript/Python
					while using concepts of Domain Driven Design.
				</p>
				<ul class='ml-4 list-disc text-muted-foreground'>
					<li>
						Led the end-to-end design and development of an event-driven notification hub that
						enabled 3 different product streams, capable of processing 100s of messages per second
						to send system-generated notifications to customers.
					</li>
					<li>
						Maintained and Enhanced the performance and robustness of an internal ETL pipeline for
						bulk API operations.
					</li>
					<li>
						Collaborated on a migration of an order management system from a single-tenant
						architecture to a multi-tenant system, optimizing cost savings for the company.
					</li>
					<li>
						Collaborated on the development of a machine-to-machine authentication system to enable
						services to perform role-based authorization.
					</li>
				</ul>
				<SectionPillButtons
					languages={['Typescript', 'Javascript', 'Python']}
					apis={apis}
					technologies={technologies}
				/>
